General Changes

1] Features Modifications:

-- Added (still higly experimental) ncurses support
-- Added subnet scan to find RIPv2 routers
-- Added the possibility to inject multiple routes
-- Added the possibility to sniff passwords

2] Code Modifications:

-- HUGE code cleanup
-- Indentation
-- Converted all the code from standard socket programming
   to libpcap and libnet. 

3] Misc Changes:

-- routemake(8) will be shipped with RiPPeR. It generates route.conf
